

an interface that will allow a random flashcard experience with chords, scales and arpeggios. 

a keyboard on the screen that shows the correct notes as green when pressed. incorrect notes show up as red

a supercollidor integration to play a nice rhodes sound. as realistic as possible. accepts midi input for user interaction 

a user history that allows for the progress of the learning to be documented and visualized 

Data models for mvp:

    * chords
    * scales
    * arpeggios
    * 